{{Quote|A Ho'Din healer never lies<br />Kibo plants cure the eyes<br />So rare and hard to find<br />For the blind man, so very kind.|[[Baji]]|<ref name="The Lost City of the Jedi">''[[The Lost City of the Jedi]]''</ref>}}
The '''Kibo''' was a rare, purple flowering [[Plant/Legends|plant]] native to [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]]. Its scent was strong and sweet and the seeds of the Kibo could restore sight.

When [[Trioculus]] attacked Yavin 4 in [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]], the fires he started brought the Kibo to the brink of extinction. Many [[Standard year/Legends|years]] later, [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] [[Chief of State (Galactic Alliance)|Chief of State]] [[Cal Omas]] kept a Kibo blossom in [[Bronzium/Legends|bronzium]] vase on his desk.

